{
  "name": "LockIn — Relances quotidiennes",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## LockIn × n8n\n\n**Variables d'environnement n8n** (Settings → Variables) :\n- `CRON_SECRET` — identique à Vercel / lockin-web\n- `LOCKIN_API_URL` — URL prod (ex. `https://app.lockin.app`)\n- `LOCKIN_FROM_EMAIL` — expéditeur SMTP\n- `TWILIO_ACCOUNT_SID` — compte Twilio\n- `TWILIO_AUTH_TOKEN` — token Twilio\n- `TWILIO_FROM_NUMBER` — numéro expéditeur SMS (E.164, ex. +33612345678)\n\n**Flux :** Cron 08h Paris → GET relances → check-status → email et/ou SMS selon `sendEmail` / `sendSms` → ack\n\n**Après import :** credentials SMTP, variables Twilio, activer le workflow, tester « Execute workflow ».",
        "height": 400,
        "width": 460,
        "color": 6
      },
      "id": "f8a1c2b3-4d5e-6f70-8192-a3b4c5d6e7f0",
      "name": "Note de configuration",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [-200, 80]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "rule": {
          "interval": [
            {
              "field": "cronExpression",
              "expression": "0 8 * * *"
            }
          ]
        },
        "timezone": "Europe/Paris"
      },
      "id": "a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ef1234567801",
      "name": "1. Tous les jours 08h00",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.scheduleTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1.2,
      "position": [240, 300]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "GET",
        "url": "={{ $env.LOCKIN_API_URL.replace(/\\/$/, '') + '/api/cron/relances-du-jour' }}",
        "authentication": "none",
        "sendHeaders": true,
        "headerParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            {
              "name": "Authorization",
              "value": "=Bearer {{ $env.CRON_SECRET }}"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {
          "response": {
            "response": {
              "fullResponse": false,
              "neverError": false
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "id": "a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ef1234567802",
      "name": "2. Récupérer relances du jour",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [520, 300]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const payload = $input.first().json;\nconst items = Array.isArray(payload?.items) ? payload.items : [];\n\nif (items.length === 0) {\n  return [];\n}\n\nreturn items.map((item) => ({ json: item }));"
      },
      "id": "a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ef1234567803",
      "name": "3. Parcourir chaque relance",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [800, 300]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "batchSize": 1,
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ef1234567804",
      "name": "4. Une relance à la fois",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.splitInBatches",
      "typeVersion": 3,
      "position": [1080, 300]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "GET",
        "url": "={{ (() => {\n  const relance = $json;\n  const ids = Array.isArray(relance.ligneIds) && relance.ligneIds.length\n    ? relance.ligneIds\n    : [relance.ligneId];\n  const query = ids.filter(Boolean).join(',');\n  return $env.LOCKIN_API_URL.replace(/\\/$/, '') + '/api/cron/check-status?ids=' + encodeURIComponent(query);\n})() }}",
        "authentication": "none",
        "sendHeaders": true,
        "headerParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            {
              "name": "Authorization",
              "value": "=Bearer {{ $env.CRON_SECRET }}"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {
